entries.s_865: [Wirartu bows.] Now you are the Arena Champion.. and rightfully so.
entries.s_867: I--I can't believe I have been defeated. You are a mighty warrior. Please... spare me. Let me live.
entries.s_871: [Wirartu bows in reverence.] You truly deserve the title of Arena Champion. You could have easily destroyed me, and yet, you spare my life. For this, I thank you. You will be known to the Kerritamba village simply as 'hero'.
